<h1>Interest Calculation</h1>
<p><strong>{{brand_name}}</strong> - {{claim_label}}</p>

<hr>

<p>
  The wizard records that the claimant wants interest considered. This sheet is a review aid and should
  be checked before filing.
</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td width="45%"><strong>Principal claim amount</strong></td>
    <td width="55%">{{currency total_claim_amount}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Reference annual rate</strong></td>
    <td>{{interest_rate}}%</td>
  </tr>
  {{#if interest_start_date}}
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Interest start date recorded</strong></td>
    <td>{{interest_start_date}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/if}}
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Reference daily interest</strong></td>
    <td>{{currency daily_interest}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>
  Interest may depend on the contract, statute, dates, and the court's discretion. The claimant should
  check the legal basis before including interest in the filed claim.
</p>
